{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"534dc62a5c","title":"关于到河南遂平调查人民公社问题给陈伯达的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"954db5c8fd","index":0,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"534dc62a5c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"08e1952454","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张春桥，当时任中共上海市委宣传部部长。"},{"id":"9f52450a9c","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘子厚，当时任中共河北省委书记处书记、河北省省长。"},{"id":"b3aca03e71","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"杭州会议，似应为郑州会议。1958年11月2日至10日，毛泽东在郑州召集了有部分中央领导人、大区负责人和部分省市委书记参加的工作会议，即第一次郑州会议。"},{"id":"44ac7afc78","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李友九，当时任《红旗》杂志常任编辑。"},{"id":"bae008be75","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指人民出版社1958年8月出版的《马克思恩格斯列宁斯大林论共产主义社会》。"},{"id":"bf1e76289b","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡绳，当时任中共中央政治研究室副主任、《红旗》杂志常任编辑。"},{"id":"7cb18ee4b9","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","index":7,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"吴冷西，当时任新华通讯社社长、《人民日报》总编辑。田家英，当时任中共中央政治研究室副主任、毛泽东的秘书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9baf187857","type":"title","text":"关于到河南送平调查人民公社问题给陈伯达的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"08e1952454","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"9f52450a9c","type":"paragraph","text":"想了一下，你和张春桥同志似以早三天去河南卫星公社进行调查工作为适宜，不必听廿一日刘子厚叫同志的报告。集中精力在卫星公社调查七天至十天，为杭州会议准备意见，很有必要。可带李友九“去帮忙。如同意，请告叶子龙同志，为你们调一架专机即飞郑州。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"b3aca03e71","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"44ac7afc78","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十九日上午七时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"bae008be75","type":"paragraph","text":"到郑州时，最好能请更向生同志和你们一道去卫星社。史对人民公社有研究，他去过卫星社。他是省委书记。伯达同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"bf1e76289b","type":"paragraph","text":"去河南时，请把《马、恩、列、斯论共产主义社会》“一书带几本去，你们调查团几个人，每人一本，边调查，边读书，白天调查，晚上阅读，有十几天，也就可以读完了。建议将胡绳、李友九都带去，练习去向劳动人民做调查工作的方法和态度，善于看问题和提问题。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"7cb18ee4b9","type":"paragraph","text":"我过了下星期就去郑州，一到，即可听你们关于卫星社观察所得的报告，在四省第一书记会议上予以讨论。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"985f63e5dd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"20a6aecc32","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十九日上午七时半","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"4ef1043c5f","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"abb166ba51","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志：","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"fa33b8e149","type":"paragraph","text":"你们调查研究卫星社大约要一个星期，包括调查团（社）营（大队）连（队）的各项问题。然后，请找遂平县级同志们座谈几次，研究全县各项问题。以上请的量处理。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"425d7e2142","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"c84c377128","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿三日下午五时","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"ebe64bab6e","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"05e6e343a6","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志：","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"59bf290edd","type":"paragraph","text":"回信收到。我还须几天才能出发。如果逐平调查已毕，你们可去附近某一个县再作几天调查，以资比较。于十一月二号或三号回到郑州即可。已令吴冷西、田家英“二同志昨日夜车出发，分赴修武七里营两处调香几关再去郑州","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"70b49bf7da","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"},{"id":"3c811256bd","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十八日上午四时","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c"}],"page":{"id":"14c8119e66","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"534dc62a5c","start":319,"end":321}}}},"__N_SSG":true}